Teaching Assistants Education
SCHOOL ADMINISTRATION POST. SSAT (Middle East) is a well-respected Consultancy, working with a large educational foundation to open a new school in Mohammed Bin Zayed City, to start in September 2014. We are seeking staff members to start work with us from early May. Applicants should send their CV, a photograph, current salary, and the names and contact details of 2 referees to: hr2@ssat.me by Monday, 5th May. State the position you are applying for in the subject line of your email. Only shortlisted candidates will be contacted, and responses will be made as CVs are received. SSAT Website: www.ssat.me | The language used in the administration will be English.Teaching Assistants - Teaching Assistants are required to support and increase student learning in the classroom, working directly with a specific group of students or individuals under the direction of the classroom teacher. A high level of English is required. A teaching degree or relevant qualification is preferable. Start August.Applicants should send their CV, a photograph, current salary, and the names and contact details of 2 referees to: hr2@ssat.me by Monday, 5th May. State the position you are applying for in the subject line of your email. Only shortlisted candidates will be contacted, and responses will be made as CVs are received. SSAT Website: www.ssat.me
